isPersistent

@GridMBeanDescription(value="Whether or not to remove data from disk.")
boolean isPersistent()
Data will not be removed from disk is this property is true.

Returns:
true if data must not be deleted at SPI stop, otherwise false.

isDeleteCorrupted

@GridMBeanDescription(value="Whether or not to delete corrupted files from disk at SPI start.")
boolean isDeleteCorrupted()
If this property is true then spi will check for corrupted files at SPI start and delete them.

Returns:
true if corrupted files should be deleted at SPI start, false otherwise.
